#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya14, sc15
msgctxt "mn5:14.1"
msgid "Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, āvuso, vijjati yaṃ idhekaccassa bhikkhuno evaṃ icchā uppajjeyya: "
